Wisebirds Bookmark is a program designed for the convenience of wisebirds employees, in korean.
It is available without being an employee, but the default bookmark may be inconvenient because it does not provide the default deletion function.


Wisebirds Bookmark is applied to the new tab buttons on the chrome,
Replace the bookmark screen provided by the existing Google Chrome with the Wisebirds Bookmark screen.

The Wisebirds Bookmark provides the following features:
time
weather
search engines
bookmark
bookmark storage

The weather is the weather provided by 'openweathermap.org' and is the weather in Seoul.

The search engine is 'www.naver.com' and 'www.google.com', which shows the search result screen using the site.

The bookmark function is provided as a basic bookmark by the basic bookmark that is frequently used by the employees in the company.
and these bookmarks are partially modified and cannot be deleted.
All bookmarks that you add are available for modification and deletion.

Images provided as basic background screens are 'vuetifyjs.com'
The background image used in the demo of the parallax component of the veetify.
